{"TopicId":126609,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"How to use the forums","CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-30T01:12:00Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Entropian","CreatedById":205453,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-30T14:20:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way to embed a Dropbox .png into a post?\u00A0 I\u0027ve tried deleting the %xxxx tag at the end and the %xx tags in the URL, but they don\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-30T17:59:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223828414\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596118835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022205453\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Entropian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Entropian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way to embed a Dropbox .png into a post?\u00A0 I\u0027ve tried deleting the %xxxx tag at the end and the %xx tags in the URL, but they don\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, the way Dropbox renames files, it is impossible to use it for a repository for your image files.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll have to use a website such as Photobucket or Imgur, or possibly host them on your own website.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Entropian","CreatedById":205453,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-30T18:19:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Entropian","CreatedById":205453,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-19T14:18:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E so Dropbox image embed actually works, you just have to change the ?dl=0 at the end to a ?dl=1.\u00A0 Example: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/dhno7aybxqcyxy0/Takeoff.png?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/dhno7aybxqcyxy0/Takeoff.png?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nversus\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Takeoff.png?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/dhno7aybxqcyxy0/Takeoff.png?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\u00A0 It might not display for some people; I\u0027m trying to narrow it down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-19T16:18:00Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2020 04:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Entropian\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-19T21:50:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223828553\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596131948\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/30/2020 at 12:59 PM, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll have to use a website such as Photobucket or Imgur, or possibly host them on your own website.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually, there is a simpler way, just paste your images in any text chat at Discord, right click it, and copy Image link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should paste into the forum just right, example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot159.png?width=756\u0026amp;height=425\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.22\u0022 height=\u0022425\u0022 width=\u0022756\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/745671718625869857/745760474800324678/screenshot159.png?width=756\u0026amp;height=425\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-19T23:02:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223840879\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597873836\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Commodoregamer118\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Commodoregamer118 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntext chat at Discord, right click it, and copy Image link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should paste into the forum just right, example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat has nothing to do with discord, but with your browser.\u00A0\u00A0 You can right click any image on the internet and click the \u0022copy image address\u0022 option.\u00A0 Note, you do not want to copy the image link in most browers, as this will copy the link to whatever the image is linked to, and not the image itself.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"B-STRK","CreatedById":126119,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-08T12:37:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure if this has been answered elsewhere here: how does one upload an Imgur-hosted video or GIF as a live player? Insert Image From URL won\u0027t do it, and neither will typing the link in the post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-08T14:22:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe forums don\u0027t seem to support MP4 direct linking.\u00A0\u00A0 Upload the video to Youtube then link that.\u00A0\u00A0 Gif\u0027s work fine, just treat them like any pic.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-22T01:53:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I post a status update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease Disregard this message, found the answer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-22T01:58:00Z\u0022 title=\u002204/22/2021 01:58  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 22, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Admiral Fluffy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceCatMeow","CreatedById":213859,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-16T20:34:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMay the Kerbal be\u00A0\u003Cspan\u003Ewith us.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-27T13:09:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSO I tried digging a little bit on this, but couldnt find anything:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nDid something change recently with Activity Streams?\u003Cbr\u003E\nI had a custom stream setup nicely, with about half of the forum sections omitted...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nRecently, my stream is now literally *FLOODED* with poo from, especially, \u0022The Lounge\u0022....\u003Cbr\u003E\nABSOLUTELY has ruined my want to even participate in the forums at all, when I have to sift thru all the garbage that single forum adds to my stream, much less all the other forums I had excluded, that I never peruse...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027ve tried poking every setting/page related to Custom Streams, but I no longer see any kind of *forum section* filtering... :screaming:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-27T13:42:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224138231\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653656955\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid something change recently with Activity Streams?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo not despair just yet.... IIRC, there is a work around for whatever change was made (I\u0027m 90% sure there is, but not 100%).\u00A0\u00A0 I do not know it, but I believe it was mentioned either in this thread or the ask the mods thread.\u00A0 Try your luck with a search (might have better luck playing keno though), but I\u0027m pretty sure somebody with the answer will come along.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-30T12:24:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E, apparently I do know how. \u00A0 Top of this page or so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002264714\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1584241609\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126609-how-to-use-the-forums/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3810137\u0026amp;embedComment=3810137\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:359px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut the fact that the picture no longer exists worries me, as I took it right from Invison\u2019s page itself. \u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-30T16:14:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224139280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653913492\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002277721\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77721-stone-blue/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Stone Blue\u003C/a\u003E, apparently I do know how. \u00A0 Top of this page or so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhhhh... Thank You!...\u003Cbr\u003E\nhmmm... I would think having \u0022Forums\u0022 shown seperately than under \u0022Topics\u0022 would have been a better choice for clarity/visibility...? vOv\u003Cbr\u003E\nbut what do *I* know?... I\u0027m just an old fart, who learned the inner-webs in the late \u002790s... :rofl:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo, IMHO: \u0022An elegant innerwebs, for a moar logical Age....\u0022 LOL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-05-30T16:16:21Z\u0022 title=\u002205/30/2022 04:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EMay 30, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T14:08:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t seem to figure out how to upload from imgur. I get the link, click insert from URL and when I click insert it just turns red. Same when I tried IBB.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T14:14:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224207337\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670681336\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t seem to figure out how to upload from imgur. I get the link, click insert from URL and when I click insert it just turns red. Same when I tried IBB.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry copying and pasting the direct link into a post, it should embed without having to use any insert functions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T14:16:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224207338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670681642\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry copying and pasting the direct link into a post, it should embed without having to use any insert functions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/27292-what-did-you-do-in-ksp-today/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4207339\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethis\u003C/a\u003E post but it\u0027s just a link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T14:22:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224207340\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022126609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670681801\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/27292-what-did-you-do-in-ksp-today/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4207339\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethis\u003C/a\u003E post but it\u0027s just a link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe forum software lost the ability to post imgur album links a while back. If you click on an image in the album and then right click and copy the image address you should end up with the direct link. You can then paste that into a post and it should embed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qKxjrSO.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qKxjrSO.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T18:19:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Imgur link version you want is the BBCode one. Imgur kept changing the way their albums linked and for a while our guys were finding work arounds, but it just got to be too much trouble so albums no longer work.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}